\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \{\cf0 \strokec3  \cf4 \strokec4 "prompt"\cf5 \strokec5 :\cf0 \strokec3  \cf6 \strokec6 "A vast dark wooden banquet table viewed from slightly above. The table fills the entire frame. On the left 80% of the table \'97 representing half of all humanity \'97 there is almost nothing at all: completely bare dark wood, one small broken bread crust in the center-left, two or three scattered crumbs, deep cold blue shadow, silence and emptiness. Absolutely no glasses, plates, or food anywhere on this side. On the far right 20% edge only \'97 representing the richest 10% of people \'97 an impossibly excessive feast is crammed and overflowing: gold-rimmed plates stacked high, grapes and figs tumbling off the edge, a tall glowing candle casting warm amber light, a full wine glass. The emotional weight is in the VASTNESS of the empty side. The feast is a tiny sliver of excess. No people, no text, no labels, no axes. Single frame. Oil painting style, cinematic dramatic lighting, magazine cover composition."\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf0 \strokec3  \cf4 \strokec4 "model"\cf5 \strokec5 :\cf0 \strokec3  \cf6 \strokec6 "Adobe Firefly 3"\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4 "dataset_name"\cf5 \strokec5 :\cf0 \strokec3  \cf6 \strokec6 "UN World Social Report 2024"\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf0 \strokec3  \cf4 \strokec4 "dataset_url"\cf5 \strokec5 :\cf0 \strokec3  \cf6 \strokec6 "https://desapublications.un.org/publications/world-social-report-2024-0"\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf0 \strokec3  \cf4 \strokec4 "insight"\cf5 \strokec5 :\cf0 \strokec3  \cf6 \strokec6 "The poorest half of humanity shares just 2% of global wealth, while the richest 10% hold 76% \'97 a disparity so extreme that half the table sits completely bare."\cf0 \strokec3  \cf2 \strokec2 \}}